            <div class="item"><span class="chk"><svg viewBox="0 0 448 512" fill="currentColor"><path d="M438.6 105.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-256 256c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0l-128-128c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0L160 338.7 393.4 105.4c12.5-12.5 32.8-12.5 45.3 0z"/></svg></span> Exportkennzeichen</div>
