              <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 512 512" fill="currentColor"><path d="M256 0a256 256 0 1 1 0 512A256 256 0 1 1 256 0zM232 120v136c0 8 4 15.5 10.7 20l96 64c11 7.4 25.9 4.4 33.3-6.7s4.4-25.9-6.7-33.3L280 243.2V120c0-13.3-10.7-24-24-24s-24 10.7-24 24z"/></svg></div>
              <div class="small">Zulassung ohne Termin</div>
              <div class="big">SOFORT VERFÜGBAR</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ════════ Ablauf / 3 Schritte ════════ -->
<section id="ablauf" class="section">
  <div class="wrap wrap-md">
    <div class="sec-head" data-aos="fade-up">
      <h2 class="h2">In 3 Schritten <span class="text-orange">ans Ziel</span></h2>
      <div class="sec-rule"></div>
      <p class="lead">Einfacher geht's nicht! Erspar dir den Weg zum Straßenverkehrsamt und nutze unseren bequemen Online-Service.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="num dark">1</div>
        <div class="ico ico-wa"><svg viewBox="0 0 576 512" fill="currentColor"><path d="M402.6 83.2 462 142.6 290 314.6l-72.2 8 8-72.2 172-167.2zM512 92.6 484.6 65.2c-12.5-12.5-32.8-12.5-45.3 0l-30.1 30.1 59.4 59.4 30.1-30.1c12.5-12.5 12.5-32.8 0-45.3zM96 64C43 64 0 107 0 160v256c0 53 43 96 96 96h256c53 0 96-43 96-96v-96c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32v96c0 17.7-14.3 32-32 32H96c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32V160c0-17.7 14.3-32 32-32h96c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32s-14.3-32-32-32H96z"/></svg></div>
        <h3 class="h3">Online Auftrag erteilen</h3>
        <p>Fülle in 2 Minuten unser Online-Formular aus, unterschreibe bequem am Bildschirm und sende uns Fotos deiner Dokumente per WhatsApp.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="num red">2</div>
        <div class="ico ico-blue"><svg viewBox="0 0 512 512" fill="currentColor"><path d="M64 0C28.7 0 0 28.7 0 64v288c0 35.3 28.7 64 64 64h176l-10.7 32H160c-17.7 0-32 14.3-32 32s14.3 32 32 32h192c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32s-14.3-32-32-32h-69.3L272 416h176c35.3 0 64-28.7 64-64V64c0-35.3-28.7-64-64-64H64zM448 64v224H64V64h384z"/></svg></div>
        <h3 class="h3">Wir lassen zu</h3>
        <p>Wir prüfen deine Dokumente sofort und führen die Online-Zulassung beim KBA für dich durch. Ohne jede Wartezeit!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="num dark">3</div>
        <div class="ico ico-orange"><svg viewBox="0 0 512 512" fill="currentColor"><path d="M135.2 117.4 109.1 192h293.8l-26.1-74.6C372.3 104.6 360.2 96 346.6 96H165.4c-13.6 0-25.7 8.6-30.2 21.4zM39.6 196.8 74.8 96.3C88.3 57.8 124.6 32 165.4 32h181.2c40.8 0 77.1 25.8 90.6 64.3l35.2 100.5c23.2 9.6 39.6 32.5 39.6 59.2v144c0 17.7-14.3 32-32 32h-32c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32v-32H96v32c0 17.7-14.3 32-32 32H32c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32V256c0-26.7 16.4-49.6 39.6-59.2zM128 288a32 32 0 1 0-64 0 32 32 0 1 0 64 0zm288 32a32 32 0 1 0 0-64 32 32 0 1 0 0 64z"/></svg></div>
        <h3 class="h3">Sofort losfahren</h3>
        <p>In unter 10 Minuten erhältst du die Bestätigung von uns und kannst direkt sicher in dein Auto steigen und losfahren.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="center" style="margin-top:48px">
      <a href={import.meta.env.BASE_URL + "/auftrag"} class="btn btn-orange glow btn-lg">
        <span class="fi"><svg viewBox="0 0 576 512" fill="currentColor"><path d="M402.6 83.2 462 142.6 290 314.6l-72.2 8 8-72.2 172-167.2zM512 92.6 484.6 65.2c-12.5-12.5-32.8-12.5-45.3 0l-30.1 30.1 59.4 59.4 30.1-30.1c12.5-12.5 12.5-32.8 0-45.3zM96 64C43 64 0 107 0 160v256c0 53 43 96 96 96h256c53 0 96-43 96-96v-96c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32s-32 14.3-32 32v96c0 17.7-14.3 32-32 32H96c-17.7 0-32-14.3-32-32V160c0-17.7 14.3-32 32-32h96c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32s-14.3-32-32-32H96z"/></svg></span>
        Jetzt Online-Auftrag starten
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

