        <div class="ic-chat"><svg viewBox="0 0 512 512" fill="currentColor"><path d="M512 240c0 114.9-114.6 208-256 208-37.1 0-72.3-6.4-104.1-17.9-11.9 8.7-31.3 20.6-54.3 30.6C73.6 471.1 44.7 480 16 480c-6.5 0-12.3-3.9-14.8-9.9s-1.1-12.9 3.4-17.4c.4-.4.8-.8 1.3-1.3 7.1-7.1 18.6-19.7 28.4-37.4 6.5-11.6 12.4-25.1 16.3-40.5C19.2 343.1 0 294.2 0 240 0 125.1 114.6 32 256 32s256 93.1 256 208z"/></svg></div>
        <h3 class="h3" style="font-size:1.5rem;margin-bottom:12px">Fragen zur Online-Zulassung?</h3>
        <p style="color:#cbd5e1;font-size:.9rem">Wir beantworten sie gern und helfen dir sofort weiter!</p>
        <div class="trust-actions">
          <a href="tel:01728474357" class="btn btn-orange glow btn-block">
            <span class="fi"><svg viewBox="0 0 512 512" fill="currentColor"><path d="M164.9 24.6c-7.7-18.6-28-28.5-47.4-23.2l-88 24C12.1 30.2 0 46 0 64 0 311.4 200.6 512 448 512c18 0 33.8-12.1 38.6-29.5l24-88c5.3-19.4-4.6-39.7-23.2-47.4l-96-40c-16.3-6.8-35.2-2.1-46.3 11.6L304.7 368C234.3 334.7 177.3 277.7 144 207.3L193.3 167c13.7-11.2 18.4-30 11.6-46.3l-40-96z"/></svg></span>
            0172 8474357
          </a>
          <a href="https://wa.me/491728474357" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-wa btn-block">
            <span class="fi"><svg viewBox="0 0 448 512" fill="currentColor"><path d="M380.9 97.1C339 55.1 283.2 32 223.9 32c-122.4 0-222 99.6-222 222 0 39.1 10.2 77.3 29.6 111L0 480l117.7-30.9c32.4 17.7 68.9 27 106.1 27h.1c122.3 0 224.1-99.6 224.1-222 0-59.3-25.2-115-67.2-157zM223.9 438.6c-33.2 0-65.7-8.9-94-25.7l-6.7-4-69.8 18.3L72 359.2l-4.4-7c-18.5-29.4-28.2-63.3-28.2-98.2 0-101.7 82.8-184.5 184.6-184.5 49.3 0 95.6 19.2 130.4 54.1 34.8 34.9 56.2 81.2 56.1 130.5 0 101.8-84.9 184.5-186.6 184.5zm101.2-138.2c-5.5-2.8-32.8-16.2-37.9-18-5.1-1.9-8.8-2.8-12.5 2.8-3.7 5.6-14.3 18-17.6 21.8-3.2 3.7-6.5 4.2-12 1.4-32.6-16.3-54-29.1-75.5-66-5.7-9.8 5.7-9.1 16.3-30.3 1.8-3.7.9-6.9-.5-9.7-1.4-2.8-12.5-30.1-17.1-41.2-4.5-10.8-9.1-9.3-12.5-9.5-3.2-.2-6.9-.2-10.6-.2-3.7 0-9.7 1.4-14.8 6.9-5.1 5.6-19.4 19-19.4 46.3 0 27.3 19.9 53.7 22.6 57.4 2.8 3.7 39.1 59.7 94.8 83.8 35.2 15.2 49 16.5 66.6 13.9 10.7-1.6 32.8-13.4 37.4-26.4 4.6-13 4.6-24.1 3.2-26.4-1.3-2.5-5-3.9-10.5-6.6z"/></svg></span>
